Class SReferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.SReferences

  • public class SReferences
extends java.lang.Object
    this is where every information about the clients is stored. It gives the number of currently playing clients, the reference of the virtual player, and the reference of the gameManager, among high granularity details
